  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deathstreak is a first-person melee action game where everyone dies in one hit. Reach your goal by overcoming enemies. Try to understand the cause and background of events. Once you reach the top of the tower, your mission will be completed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies with Melee weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/79ef2182b39f261b705e839298d719b5.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/79ef2182b39f261b705e839298d719b5.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/79ef2182b39f261b705e839298d719b5.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/ac628ba148d87a9cf6e2e17f3d3b4239.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/ac628ba148d87a9cf6e2e17f3d3b4239.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/ac628ba148d87a9cf6e2e17f3d3b4239.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies with Blades attached to your arms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/80096e4a98412d9d97d0c70e72194454.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/80096e4a98412d9d97d0c70e72194454.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/80096e4a98412d9d97d0c70e72194454.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/6a7afee38b25c2ed4613cc3a730cfe33.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/6a7afee38b25c2ed4613cc3a730cfe33.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/6a7afee38b25c2ed4613cc3a730cfe33.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/84911bb229261468a768465b69d5a1e2.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/84911bb229261468a768465b69d5a1e2.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/84911bb229261468a768465b69d5a1e2.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill those who stand in your way with the throwables you collect from the environment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/0277d8577f5f7187c2958a0fc9ba3912.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/0277d8577f5f7187c2958a0fc9ba3912.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/0277d8577f5f7187c2958a0fc9ba3912.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill enemies before they have a chance to attack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/4c5d503b3a56ec2435a6b9343436d3d6.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/4c5d503b3a56ec2435a6b9343436d3d6.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/4c5d503b3a56ec2435a6b9343436d3d6.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cling to walls to overcome obstacles and reach enemies in different ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/734ea940cb1821df3633d66576442029.poster.avif?t=1762966227\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/734ea940cb1821df3633d66576442029.webm?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355960/extras/734ea940cb1821df3633d66576442029.mp4?t=1762966227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
